      "order": 1,
      "instruction": "Dressing: Shake Dressing ingredients in a jar."
    },
    {
      "order": 2,
      "instruction": "Toss! Place cabbage, fennel, apple and dill in a very large bowl. Pour over Dressing, toss well."
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "instruction": "Sprinkle with caraway seeds then toss again."
    },
    {
      "order": 4,
      "instruction": "Set aside for at least 1 hour to allow cabbage to wilt. Give it a good toss, then transfer to serving bowl and serve!"
    },
    {
      "order": 5,
      "instruction": "Storage: Keeps perfecty for 3 to 4 days in the fridge. Dressing stops apple from going brown. Best to bring to room temperature before serving."
